<title type="html"><![CDATA[12/30 (Thu.) Break up and Maintain a Relationship/New Year Resolution (Host: Julia Ho)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=577&amp;p=600#p600"><![CDATA[
30 December 2021 (Thu.) Break up and Maintain a Relationship/New Year Resolution (Host: Julia Ho)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #800000">We hold a hybrid meeting on Thursday:<br /><br />On-site meeting:<br />Dante coffee 丹堤 臺北市大安區濟南路三段25號 忠孝新生 MRT Exit 3<br /><br />On-line meeting:<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233</span></span><br /><br /><br />Session One<br />Leehom Wang apologizes, vows to take break from entertainment<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://focustaiwan.tw/society/202112200020">https://focustaiwan.tw/society/202112200020</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.verywellmind.com/how-to-end-a-relationship-4173954">https://www.verywellmind.com/how-to-end ... ip-4173954</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />1.Do you know any of your relatives/friends/colleagues/classmates who used to have extramarital affairs or it is still ongoing? According to your observation, what is the percentage of married couples who encounter the problem?<br /><br />2.What are the benefits and costs of a romantic relationship? Are you happy being single or in a relationship?<br /><br />3. How to break up with someone in the kindest possible way?<br /><br />4.How to build a happy and long-lasting relationship? <br /><br />………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………<br /><br />Session Two<br />The New Year's Resolution to Make When Everything Feels Out of Your Control<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://time.com/6125635/new-years-resolution-2022-help-others/">https://time.com/6125635/new-years-reso ... lp-others/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.Do you think that almost everything is out of control in 2021? Can you name some?<br /><br />2.What are the major things happened in your life in 2021? What are the happiest moments? What are the most miserable/challenging moments? What’s the best lesson you have learned in 2021?<br /><br />3.What’s your prediction for 2022? What’s your suggestion to embrace 2022?<br /><br />4.What’s your expectation to your own 2022? What are your new year's resolutions?<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情的心，參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=37037">JuliaHo</a> — Thu Dec 23, 2021 10:17 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
